No. 11-122. Innovair Aviation Limited, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1147, 132 S. Ct. 999,

181 L. Ed. 2d 790,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 567. January 9, 2012.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice and Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 632 F.3d 1336.
